Class RentsController

java.lang.Object
com.ktzvhad.rents.controller.RentsController
@RestController @RequestMapping("/rents") @CrossOrigin(origins="http://localhost:8080") public class RentsController extends Object
Controller class for handling rental and donation data. Provides endpoints for various operations related to rents and donations.
